\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Review Materials:} Study advanced VoIP configurations and network security in virtualization.
    \item \textbf{Skill Development:} Practice troubleshooting network and SIP-related issues.
    \item \textbf{Preparatory Tasks:} Research integration of FreePBX with external VoIP providers.
\end{itemize}



 

